</tr>
</table>
<p><a name="Minor_Provinces" id="Minor_Provinces"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=British_Raj&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Minor Provinces">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Minor Provinces</span></h3>
<p>In addition, there were a few minor provinces that were administered by a Chief Commissioner:<sup id="cite_ref-igi-56_12-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-igi-56-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
