<td>Mortalities in <a href="/wiki/Bihar_famine_of_1873%E2%80%9374" title="Bihar famine of 1873–74">Bihar famine of 1873–74</a> prevented by importation of rice from Burma.<br />
Gaikwad of Baroda dethroned for misgovernment; dominions continued to a child ruler.<br />
Indian Councils Act of 1874<br />
Visit of the <a href="/wiki/Prince_of_Wales" title="Prince of Wales">Prince of Wales</a>, future <a href="/wiki/Edward_VII" title="Edward VII" class="mw-redirect">Edward VII</a> in 1875–76.</td>
