Bubonic plague in Bombay (1896), Bubonic plague in Calcutta (1898); riots in wake of plague prevention measures.<br />
Establishment of Provincial Legislative Councils in <a href="/wiki/Burma" title="Burma">Burma</a> and Punjab; the former a new Lieutenant Governorship.</td>
