<a href="/wiki/Delhi_Durbar" title="Delhi Durbar">Coronation Durbar in Delhi (1903)</a>; <a href="/wiki/Edward_VII" title="Edward VII" class="mw-redirect">Edward VII</a> (in absentia) proclaimed <a href="/wiki/Emperor_of_India" title="Emperor of India">Emperor of India</a>.<br />
