<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Oxford English Dictionary, 2nd edition, 1989. "b. spec. the British dominion or rule in the Indian sub-continent (before 1947). In full, <i>British raj</i>.</li>
