<p><a name="Contemporary_general_histories" id="Contemporary_general_histories"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=British_Raj&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Contemporary general histories">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Contemporary general histories</span></h3>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;-moz-column-count:3; -webkit-column-count:3; column-count:3;">
<ul>
