1922–1961 &#160;<a href="/wiki/Tanganyika_Territory" title="Tanganyika Territory">Tanganyika <small><i>(Tanzania)</i></small></a>&#160;<sup><small>5</small></sup><br />
1954–1960 &#160;<i><a href="/wiki/Nigeria" title="Nigeria">Nigeria</a></i><br /></p>
</td>
